      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777404602814,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- Library that you share with others - LOTS of tests. Speculative.\n    - UI - used by ~100 \n    - detect breaking stuff for the consumers of your library.\n        - low level unit tests\n        - Playwright - (not Component Testing) - Cypress Component\n\n\n- Application means you KNOW how the code is going to be used.\n   - your tests should always be based on actual use of the application.\n        - probably something like playwright is going to be 98% of your tests.\n\n\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Library that you share with others - LOTS of tests. Speculative.\n    - UI - used by ~100 \n    - detect breaking stuff for the consumers of your library.\n        - low level unit tests\n        - Playwright - (not Component Testing) - Cypress Component\n\n\n- Application means you KNOW how the code is going to be used.\n   - your tests should always be based on actual use of the application.\n        - probably something like playwright is going to be 98% of your tests.\n\n\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "YjHlpJENuv-f8c8RGae0R",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -112.41001892089844,
